<item>
            <title>[MJAVADOC-133] Javadoc fails if footer contains newlines</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MJAVADOC-133</link>
                <project id="12317529" key="MJAVADOC">Maven Javadoc Plugin (Moved to GitHub Issues)</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The current version of the javadoc plugin fails if the footer specified for the project contains newline characters:&lt;/p&gt;

